songs.title: Who’s That Girl?
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
I remember when loving you was so fine
We would spend all our time as one
Now you're treating me as if I'm second-best
And got me feeling stressed
Oh, how come?

[Chorus]
Who's that girl with eyes for you?
Who's that girl with eyes for you?
(Eyes for you, my baby)

[Verse 2]
I thought this would last forever, but
It seems perhaps I was a fool
The thoughts of losing you been in my mind
Who's taking up my time with you?

[Chorus]
So who's that girl with eyes for you?
(Eyes on you)
Who's that girl with eyes for you?
(Eyes on my man, uh-huh)

[Bridge]
If you don't cherish me, baby please use honesty
Don't continue to lie and live in secrecy
I gave to you my world, in case you didn't know
So the least you can do, tell me, who is that girl?

[Chorus]
Who's that girl with eyes for you?
Who's that girl with eyes for you?
(I can't hear you)
Who's that girl with eyes for you?
Who's that girl with eyes for you?
(Tell her to go)

[Outro]
My eyes do see her eyes on...
My eyes do see...
Lellow, Krucial, H.E., baby, Mr. Brown, what what
